    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/c6be1dd7287ad00040ba26ee7950ad93.poster.avif?t=1751050837\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/c6be1dd7287ad00040ba26ee7950ad93.webm?t=1751050837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/c6be1dd7287ad00040ba26ee7950ad93.mp4?t=1751050837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>WARRIORS</strong> 是一款为多人游戏和单人游戏（带有AI机器人）设计的射击游戏。购买抢先体验的玩家将立即解锁所有武器皮肤和角色。后续解锁将通过积累经验值完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前，游戏提供8种模式：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>征服模式（CONQUEST）</strong><br>控制目标点以随着时间积累积分。你的团队控制的目标点越多，得分速度越快。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>突击模式（RUSH）</strong><br>摧毁或防守目标点。如果进攻方用尽了增援，则防守方获胜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>确认击杀（KILL CONFIRMED）</strong><br>击杀敌方玩家并收集他们的身份牌以获得积分。同时，你也可以收集队友的身份牌以阻止对方得分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>团队死亡竞赛（TEAM DEATHMATCH）</strong><br>击杀敌方玩家以获得积分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>夺旗模式（CAPTURE THE FLAG）</strong><br>夺取敌方旗帜并将其带回基地以得分。如果你的旗帜被夺走，必须先夺回它。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由混战（FREE FOR ALL）</strong><br>击杀所有其他玩家以获得积分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>搜索与摧毁（SEARCH AND DESTROY）</strong><br>在时间耗尽之前摧毁目标。每名玩家每回合只有一次生命。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>僵尸模式（ZOMBIE）</strong><br>与可怕的僵尸战斗。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/e7d34dfb345900f8b37fdec5cd15b063.poster.avif?t=1751050837\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/e7d34dfb345900f8b37fdec5cd15b063.webm?t=1751050837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/e7d34dfb345900f8b37fdec5cd15b063.mp4?t=1751050837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感源于最优秀的FPS游戏，<strong>WARRIORS</strong> 提供了多样化的游戏模式和地图——无论你是喜欢小型竞技场的紧张近距离战斗，还是更大的地图上的策略性战斗。游戏拥有流畅的多人功能、多样的武器选择以及用于离线练习的AI机器人，提供快速而响应迅速的游戏体验，同时避免了不必要的复杂性。社区托管的服务器更进一步丰富了体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/94d8a2c271e44e55c9e0942c6a8b326f.poster.avif?t=1751050837\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/94d8a2c271e44e55c9e0942c6a8b326f.webm?t=1751050837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153790/extras/94d8a2c271e44e55c9e0942c6a8b326f.mp4?t=1751050837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将在不同规模的地图上体验紧张的战斗场景。参与小型地图上的快速枪战，这些地图为快节奏、高强度的对战而设计。而对于那些寻求更广阔战场的人来说，大型地图提供了策略性玩法，包括战术机动、狙击手位置以及协调的团队攻击。不论你的游戏风格如何，<strong>WARRIORS</strong> 都有适合你的地图。</p>",
